{"tid":1970684,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"你哋係咪唔記得今日係咩日子？全部人同我入哂黎！！！！！","createTime":"2020-04-13T10:29:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T01:20:27.000Z","uid":73381,"like":8,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d5894b7799ae2f75678a79c7b04c21218fa11569","tid":1970684,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WaOqgbw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWaOqgbw.png&h=23e05550&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我屌哂你哋老母！今日係達哥關注事件十個月紀念日！竟然冇人記得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋係咪想輸？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f71e657e27f7347be8364910a22db481675a39","tid":1970684,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WeEnxMP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWeEnxMP.png&h=4c3e1bf2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ab3bbaf514345c19863a7f891c510687e2dec9c","tid":1970684,"uid":32454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:32:03.000Z","msg":"想同達哥親口講聲對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5afddcb6f8c4827f2c5163a590d5dd45e8602236","tid":1970684,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"0ab3bbaf514345c19863a7f891c510687e2dec9c","tid":1970684,"uid":32454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:32:03.000Z","msg":"想同達哥親口講聲對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:33:35.000Z","msg":"六月，對達哥感到失望。<br />\n七月，對達哥感到憤怒。<br />\n八月，對達哥感到可惜。<br />\n九月，些少懷念每晚睇開台既日子。<br />\n十月，開始睇番達哥每晚既重播。<br />\n十一月，很想念他。<br />\n十二月，默默為達哥打氣。<br />\n一月了，開始後悔當初為何要逼達哥。<br />\n二月了，想跟達哥親口說句「對不起」。<br />\n三月了，擔心達哥夠不夠口罩用。<br />\n四月了，達哥，對不起。"},{"pid":"33cd0ac5608a7adcb4d5ed39c5dcca6ac9e03abf","tid":1970684,"uid":15658,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:34:24.000Z","msg":"hi大j   d沙律錢用哂未"},{"pid":"4cff72f597366ebcf2f730c60d3481b948ccd4a5","tid":1970684,"uid":106348,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2f71e657e27f7347be8364910a22db481675a39","tid":1970684,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WeEnxMP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWeEnxMP.png&h=4c3e1bf2&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:37:02.000Z","msg":"圈錯咗  達哥一早預知今年會有疫情 佢係講&quot;康復香港&quot;"},{"pid":"e52566a12a614e58dfd1092117d45036e4184ae7","tid":1970684,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4cff72f597366ebcf2f730c60d3481b948ccd4a5","tid":1970684,"uid":106348,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2f71e657e27f7347be8364910a22db481675a39","tid":1970684,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WeEnxMP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWeEnxMP.png&h=4c3e1bf2&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:37:02.000Z","msg":"圈錯咗  達哥一早預知今年會有疫情 佢係講&quot;康復香港&quot;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:39:28.000Z","msg":"達哥係全香港<br />\n1. 第一個提出以光復香港作為口號<br />\n2. 第一個提出以康復香港作為口號<br />\n3. 第一個實行罷工<br />\n4. 想知再講"},{"pid":"c104d3cf3734f9e0cc8a5e7fe109b129b8db38fe","tid":1970684,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"33cd0ac5608a7adcb4d5ed39c5dcca6ac9e03abf","tid":1970684,"uid":15658,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:34:24.000Z","msg":"hi大j   d沙律錢用哂未"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:41:51.000Z","msg":"你噏乜柒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\"